    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Right at Home Winnipeg - Complete Social Media Automation\n\n### Workflow Overview\nThis workflow automates the entire social media posting process:\n1. **Runs 3x weekly** (Mon/Wed/Fri at 8 AM)\n2. **Fetches topic** from Google Sheets calendar\n3. **Generates content** using AI (GPT-4)\n4. **Creates visuals** using DALL-E 3\n5. **Approval process** via web form\n6. **Posts to Facebook & Instagram**\n7. **Tracks everything** in Google Sheets\n\n### Setup Required:\n1. Replace all placeholder IDs:\n   - `YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID`\n   - `YOUR_FACEBOOK_PAGE_ID`\n   - `YOUR_INSTAGRAM_BUSINESS_ID`\n   - `YOUR_SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL`\n   \n2. Set up credentials:\n   - Google Sheets OAuth2\n   - OpenAI API\n   - Facebook Graph API\n   \n3. Create Google Sheets with tabs:\n   - Content Calendar\n   - Post History\n   - Error Log\n\n### Cost Estimate:\n- ~$2-3/month for AI usage\n- 3 posts/week = 12-15 posts/month",
        "height": 600,
        "width": 400,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "b73a8c49-7c7b-4a90-a3c5-ca25f87bd400",
      "name": "Workflow Documentation",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -944,
        -288
      ]
    }
